{"title":"Hexo博客搭建","slug":"Hexo博客搭建","date":"2019-07-26T06:48:35.000Z","updated":"2019-07-27T07:25:06.149Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo博客搭建.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"1、关于Hexo搭建教程网络上有许多。<br>环境配置、百度收录等等，<br>以下是稍微全面一点的：","covers":null,"content":"<p>1、关于Hexo搭建教程网络上有许多。<br>环境配置、百度收录等等，<br>以下是稍微全面一点的：</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>TDsimon的：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/simon__he/article/details/83715511\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点我</a><br>grave2015的：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/grave2015/article/details/79961843\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点我</a></p>\n<p>在使用主题时首先看官方文档。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install </span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>2、当在使用npm时速度过慢或者没有速度时，可换为淘宝镜像<br>菜鸟教程方法：<a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/nodejs/nodejs-npm.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点我</a><br>或斐鸽传书的简书<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/1a426b889bad\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点我</a></p>\n<p>3、使用Markdown写博客<br>Markdown语法：<a href=\"http://xianbai.me/learn-md/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点我</a></p>\n<p>4、部署到Github上时修改_config.yml的deploy:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    type:</span> <span class=\"string\">git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    repo:</span> <span class=\"attr\">https://github.com/Yourname/Yourname.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    branch:</span> <span class=\"string\">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>5、配置SSH Key时<br><code>/c/Users/you/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</code><br>无法打开，使用word或记事本即可。</p>\n<p>6、删除Blog目录重装部署时的报错</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d </span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Deployer not found: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git  //重装下</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>7、此主题为Lite，感谢作者。</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}]}